{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/XcodePreviewSupport","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"role":"article","title":"Xcode Preview Support","roleHeading":"Article","modules":[{"name":"Forge"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Architecture and Best Practices","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/ModularArchitecture","doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/SOLIDPrinciples"],"anchor":"Architecture-and-Best-Practices"}],"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provide preview-safe mock factories that activate automatically in Xcode Previews."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dependencies that hit the network, access the file system, or perform heavy"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"computation are problematic in Xcode Previews. Forge lets you provide a "},{"code":"preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"factory that is used automatically when running inside a preview — no conditional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"checks needed in your view code.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"The-preview-Parameter","text":"The preview Parameter"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pass a "},{"code":"preview","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" closure to "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Forge\/documentation\/Forge\/Container\/provide(_:preview:key:_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" alongside the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"normal factory:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["public var authService: any AuthServiceProtocol {","    provide(.singleton, preview: { MockAuthService() }) {","        AuthService(network: self.